com.amazonaws.services.sqs
Interface AmazonSQSAsync

All Superinterfaces:
AmazonSQS
All Known Implementing Classes:
AmazonSQSAsyncClient, AmazonSQSBufferedAsyncClient
public interface AmazonSQSAsync
extends AmazonSQS

Interface for accessing AmazonSQS asynchronously. Each asynchronous method will return a Java Future object, and users are also allowed to provide a callback handler.
